data.enText: a small bed with high sides for a baby or young child
a travel cot (= one that can be moved around easily, used when travelling)

tr: a small bed that folds up for storage or transport
baby bed with high sides made of slats
a sheath worn to protect a finger

value.def: A cot is a bed for a baby, with bars or panels round it so that the baby cannot fall out.

value.boxr_value: in AM, use 美国英语用 crib

value.def: A cot is a narrow bed, usually made of canvas fitted over a frame which can be folded up.

value.boxr_value: in BRIT, use 英国英语用 camp bed
